CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 4, 1956, pg. A12 reads: ""Feted At Garden Party - Among the 70 persons attending the garden party given by Mrs. A. Owens at her home on Copeland St. were the following guests from Detroit, Mich. Left to right: Mmes. Delia Carnes, Suza Gordon, Willie Mae Cook, Cecelia Blevins, Florence Beard and N. Yates. - "Teenie" Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of garden party guests, from left: Delia Carnes, Suza Gordon, Willie Mae Cook, Cecelia Blevins, Florence Beard, and Mrs. N. Yates, posed in dining room in home of Mrs. A. Owens, Copeland Street
